Jab se maine tujhko hai jaana 
Tab se chaaha tujhko hai paana 
Ga raha hoon main kyun ye gaana 
Main na jaanu O jaane jaana Dil bhi mera kehna na maana 
Milne ka tujhse dhoondhe bahana 
Tera mera banta fasaana 
Chaahe job hi soche zamaana Teri yaadon ki baarishon me 
Shikwe saare ye dhul gaye 
Tujhse milne ki khwahishon me 
Khud se bhi hum na mil sake Mil gayi hain wo raahein 
Tujhe dhundhta firoon 
Faili hain meri baahein 
Par nahi hai tu Tu hi bata-Tuhi bata-Tu hi bata 
Dil ki khata 
Tu hi bata-Tuhi bata-Tu hi bata 
Manzil ka pata Sapno mein aake tum 
Neendein meri udaa jaati ho 
Dil me bas ke tum 
Dhadkan meri churaa jaati ho Dooriyaan jab bhi tumko, ye satayeingi 
Khalish banke main tumko yaad aaunga 
Jab bhi tumko meri yaad aayegi 
Ashq banke main tere paas aaunga Tere hasne ki aahaton mein 
Dard saare ye bhul gaye 
Tumse to hum mil gaye par 
Dil se dil ye na mil sake Mil gayi hain wo raahein 
Tujhe dhundhta firoon 
Faili hain meri baahein 
Par nahi hai tu Tu hi bata-Tuhi bata-Tu hi bata 
Dil ki khata 
Tu hi bata-Tuhi bata-Tu hi bata 
Manzil ka pata Teri yaadon ke angaaron pe chalke 
Teri chaahat ke sholon mein bhi jalke 
Ankhon se jo aansu mere chalke 
Unse maine ye kaha Tu hi bata-Tuhi bata-Tu hi bata 
Dil ki khata 
Tu hi bata-Tuhi bata-Tu hi bata 
Manzil ka pata